BITMAPS={0,526472,340,1439220,1879374,461880,739656,136,297092,541768,1236690,40064,1081344,7168,524288,1116228,867180,279748,2000172,1846332,147250,1850654,867596,279614,863532,798508,32896,557184,299140,115136,1082512,526424,988972,1261356,1916220,864556,1913660,2039070,1121566,866060,1261362,559240,860706,1268050,2035984,1258482,1259442,865068,1121596,1012524,1269052,1846542,559260,865074,611668,1307442,1256754,559444,2034750,821388,280848,803916,328,1966080,72,1261356,1916220,864556,1913660,2039070,1121566,866060,1261362,559240,860706,1268050,2035984,1258482,1259442,865068,1121596,1012524,1269052,1846542,559260,865074,611668,1307442,1256754,559444,2034750,825484,557192,1608856,5280,0} PM={} PMS={}
function compile() for _,bm in pairs(BITMAPS) do pm={} for y=1,5 do pm[y]={} for x=1,4 do pm[y][x] = ( bm & (2^((y-1)*4+5-x)) ) == (2^((y-1)*4+5-x)) end end PM[_] = pm end end
compile()
function generatePixelMapForSize(pm,size) pms={} for y=1,5*size do for x=1,4*size do if pm[math.floor(0.5+y/size)] and pm[math.floor(0.5+y/size)][math.floor(0.5+x/size)] then table.insert(pms,{x=x,y=y}) end end end return pms end
function drawChar(px,py,c,size)--size: 1=normal id = string.byte(c)-31
if not PM[id] then return end
if not PMS[id] then PMS[id]={} end
if not PMS[id][size] then PMS[id][size]=generatePixelMapForSize(PM[id],size) end
for _,p in pairs(PMS[id][size]) do screen.drawRectF(px+p.x, py+p.y, 1, 1) end end
function drawText(x,y,text,size) if size == nil or size == 1 then screen.drawText(x,y,text) end
for i=1,string.len(text) do drawChar(x+(i-1)*5*size, y, string.sub(text, i, i+1), size) end end
myid="-"
function onTick() if input.getNumber(32) > 0 then myid = input.getNumber(32) end end
function onDraw() screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawClear() screen.setColor(0, 0, 255) text="#"..math.floor(myid) drawText(screen.getWidth()/2-(string.len(text)*10/2.2),screen.getHeight()/2-5,text,2) end

object.script:
-- ch1n: selected id -- ch2n: unusable! -- ch 1-7b: power leds of rack slots 1-7 (blinking = boot, permanent on = on, permanent off = off) -- ch10b: enable status of selected -- ch10n: type of selected (1=server,2=storage,3=router) -- ch31b: unusable! -- ch:20-24 => monitor touch input -- ch25:b default enable state -- 26n: loading screen opacity
racks={}
currentRackId=1
firstPress=true
opac=255 function onTick() screenon=input.getBool(20) if screenon and opac > 0 then opac=opac-2 end if not screenon then opac=255 end output.setNumber(26,opac)
maxRackId=input.getNumber(2)-1
-- send enabled information output.setBool(10, (racks[currentRackId] and racks[currentRackId].enabled) == true) output.setNumber(1,currentRackId)
-- receive status information id = input.getNumber(11) if not racks[id] then racks[id] = {enabled=input.getBool(25)} end racks[id].slots={ input.getBool(1), input.getBool(2), input.getBool(3), input.getBool(4), input.getBool(5), input.getBool(6), input.getBool(7) } racks[id].type=input.getNumber(10)
if currentRackId < maxRackId then currentRackId = currentRackId + 1 else currentRackId = 1 end
press=input.getBool(21) pressx=input.getNumber(20) pressy=input.getNumber(21)
scrlup=false scrldown=false
if isPressing(SW-10,0,10,10) then scroll=scroll-1 scrlup=true end if isPressing(SW-10,SH-10,10,10) then scroll=scroll+1 scrldown=true end
for i=1,maxRackId do if isPressing(SW-30,HEIGHT_PER_RACK*(i-1)-scroll+1,17,10) and firstPress then racks[i].enabled = not racks[i].enabled end end
if scroll < 0 then scroll=0 end if HEIGHT_PER_RACK*#racks<SH then scroll=0 elseif scroll > HEIGHT_PER_RACK*#racks-SH then scroll=HEIGHT_PER_RACK*#racks-SH end
if not press then firstPress=true elseif firstPress then firstPress = false end end
scroll=0 scrlup=false scrldown=false
HEIGHT_PER_RACK=14
SW=0 SH=0
function onDraw() S=screen SW=S.getWidth() SH=S.getHeight()
S.setColor(0,0,0) S.drawClear()
widthPerSlot=(SW-32)/7
--draw racks for id=1,maxRackId do r=racks[id] if r then y=HEIGHT_PER_RACK*(id-1)-scroll if y > -HEIGHT_PER_RACK and y < SH then --check visibility S.setColor(11,28,29) S.drawRectF(0,y,SW,HEIGHT_PER_RACK-1) S.setColor(80,80,80) S.drawText(1,y+1,"#"..id) S.drawText(3+string.len("#"..id)*5,y+1, getType(r.type))
if widthPerSlot > 14 then for s=1,7 do S.setColor(0,0,0) S.drawText(1+widthPerSlot*(s-1), y+7, "s"..s) if r.slots[s] then S.setColor(0,255,0) else S.setColor(255,0,0) end S.drawRectF(1+widthPerSlot*(s-1)+10, y+8, 3,3) end else for s=1,7 do if r.slots[s] then S.setColor(0,255,0) else S.setColor(255,0,0) end S.drawText(1+widthPerSlot*(s-1), y+7, "s"..s) end end
--button if r.enabled then S.setColor(0,120,0) text="ON" else S.setColor(120,0,0) text="OFF" end S.drawRectF(SW-30,HEIGHT_PER_RACK*(id-1)-scroll+1,17,10) S.setColor(0,0,0) S.drawRect(SW-30,HEIGHT_PER_RACK*(id-1)-scroll+1,17,10) S.drawTextBox(SW-29,HEIGHT_PER_RACK*(id-1)-scroll+1,17,11,text,0,0) end end end
--scroll if scrlup then S.setColor(80,80,0) else S.setColor(80,0,0) end S.drawTriangleF(SW-10,10, SW-5,0,SW,10)
if scrldown then S.setColor(80,80,0) else S.setColor(80,0,0) end S.drawTriangleF(SW-10,SH-10, SW-5,SH,SW,SH-10) end
function getType(n) if n==1 then return "server" elseif n==2 then return "storage" elseif n==3 then return "router" else return "unknown" end end
function isPressing(x,y,w,h) return press and pressx >= x and pressx <= x+w and pressy >= y and pressy <= y+h end
